       title="PHP-GPT" id="PHP-GPT">

    <p>
        A PHP library that infuses the magic of OpenAI's GPT, with PHP.
    </p>
    <p>
        Offering a simple and elegant interface using a fluid design and a smart approach to
        working with responses, PHP-GPT makes working with AI simple.
    </p>
    <code-block lang="php">
        echo AI::chat('Tell me a joke');
    </code-block>
    <p>
        Offering a wide range of services.
    </p>
    <p>
        Such as text to speech.
    </p>
    <code-block lang="php">
        $mp3FilePath = (string) AI::createSpeech('Hello, how are you?');
    </code-block>
    <p>
        Or image generation.
    </p>
    <code-block lang="php">
        $imageUrl = (string) AI::createImage('A cute picture of a fox');
    </code-block>
    <p>
        Packed with features such as image and document analyse, streaming, assistant creation
        and management.
    </p>
    <p>
        And the more powerful features such as deeply integrating your PHP application with AI
        allowing AI to execute your code to complete the tasks you have given it.
    </p>
</topic>